1 月可能重返白宫，这些议题都是欧盟此刻面临的重大挑战。 法国总统马克龙当地时间 5 月 26 日发表讲话 马克龙：欧盟正经历「内外部敌人」引发的「民主危机」，最终可能会「彻底消亡」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f27996c1d15fcaa379e2b0a7a94969e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "37 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657305708"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI3YfN+daIsLN/EAMaCTEwODM0NTg0NyDJ18+yBjAAOI8BQC1yCTY1NzMwNTcwOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1716863110.945651", "card_id": "Q_657357738", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价电视剧《庆余年第二季》第 23-24 集？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-7192c9f1e0818044046ac75ebe9e9425_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "37 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657357738"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3YfN+daIsLN/EAMaCTEwODM1NzQwNyCW29GyBjAAOCBALnIJNjU3MzU3NzM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1716863110.945903", "card_id": "Q_657304316", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "1~4 月份全国规模以上工业企业利润增长 4.3%，这一数据说明了什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "每经 AI 快讯，国家统计局数据显示，1~4 月份，全国规模以上工业企业实现利润总额 20946.9 亿元，同比增长 4.3%（按可比口径计算，详见附注二）。1~4 月份，规模以上工业企业中，国有控股企业实现利润总额 7396.4 亿元，同比下降 2.8%；股份制企业实现利润总额 15508.1 亿元，增长 0.9%；外商及港澳台投资企业实现利润总额 5285.9 亿元，增长 16.7%；私营企业实现利润总额 5448.0 亿元，增长 6.4%。国家统计局：1~4 月份全国规模以上工业企业利润增长 4.3% | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-8c2ddaaa67c80803798a28412ffc77a5_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "37 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color"